<div class="pl6-ns pr6-ns pt5-ns  pt4">
  <h1 class="fw4-ns f1-ns f2 fw5  pl3 pr3 orange">
    Get Involved
  </h1>

  <p class="f2-l fw3-l f4 pl3 pr3 ">
    <span class="courier">:bgt</span> wouldn't be what it is now without the help of our supporters and those around who have offered their time, money and services to help us grow. If you would like to get involved and support us, find out how below.
  </p>

  <div class="f2-l fl-l w-100-l f4 tc">
    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-heart-o pink-local white-ns" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw;"></i>
      <h2 class="grow dim f2">
        <%= link_to "Volunteer", volunteer_path, class: "pink-local white-ns" %>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-pencil pink-local white-ns" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw;"></i>
      <h2 class="grow dim f2">
        <%= link_to "Contribute", contribute_path, class: "pink-local white-ns" %>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-money pink-local white-ns" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw;"></i>
      <h2 class="grow dim f2">
        <%= link_to "Donate", donate_path, class: "pink-local white-ns" %>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
